Music Club | Freshie Solo | 1-11-16(Tuesday) 6PM | HSB 356

Body:
Freshies!

You survived two Quizzes, so congratulations on making it this far! And
now, we give you the chance to let off some steam AND show us your diverse
musical talents on stage, with FRESHIE SOLO! Come on down to HSB 356 at 6
P.M. tomorrow, and bring your vocal and/or your instrumental talents with
you!

Date: 1st November, 2016
Venue: HSB 356
Time: 6 p.m.

Rules:

1) Songs can be sung in any language. This is a Western Music and Light
Music combined event.

2)The maximum time limit you can take for a solo performance is 4 minutes.

3) Freshies of all courses (B. Tech, DD, MA, M. Tech, Phd, MBA, MS) can
participate.

4)Karaoke or one accompaniment is permitted.Please bring your karaoke track
in a pendrive and give it to us while registering.

5) You must bring your own instruments; however, a drum kit will be
provided at the venue.

Registrations are done on spot.

IITM Music Club



